## 关于资源文件的补充说明 (Asset Files Notice)

assets/ 目录中的地理数据（historical-china/、historical-world/、
hillshade/、timelines/）基于以下开源数据集加工而成：

- CHGIS (Harvard China Historical GIS) — CC-BY 4.0
- Natural Earth — Public Domain
- 各朝代时间线数据整理自公开历史文献

使用 assets/ 中的数据时，请保留原始数据集的署名要求。

The data in assets/ is derived from:
- CHGIS (Harvard China Historical GIS) — CC-BY 4.0
- Natural Earth — Public Domain
- Dynasty timelines compiled from public historical sources

When using assets/, please retain the attribution of the original datasets.
